{"product_id":"magrada-lip-balm-melissa-10g","title":"Magrada Lip Balm Melissa 10g","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"Body\"\u003eThe wonderful lemon balm is a powerful natural herb which refreshes your lips as well as your senses with its spirited midsummer aroma.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"Body\"\u003eThe silky lip balm cools, smooths, moisturises, and nurtures, adding the effect of healthy and plump lips as a bonus.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eValuable\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eorganic lemon balm oil\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003ewith its fresh herbal scent calms your skin and your senses.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"Default\"\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eOrganic shea butter \u003c\/span\u003eis characterised by a higher concentration of fatty acids and vitamins. The butter, which originates from Africa, is also known for its anti-inflammatory properties.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"Default\"\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eOrganic castor oil\u003c\/span\u003e helps to preserve the moisture level of the lips and prevents the loss of moisture through the upper layer of the skin.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"Default\"\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eOrganic cocoa butter\u003c\/span\u003e as a cold-pressed oil is a powerful source of Vitamin E.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"Default\"\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eOrganic olive oil\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003eis a perfect moisturiser for dry lips.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eThe creamy lip butter is suitable for daily use. To treat chapped lips, we recommend using a lip balm just before going to bed.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eOlea Europaea Fruit Oil, Cera Alba*, Theobroma Cacao Seed Butter*, Hydrogenated Vegetable Oil, Ricinus Communis Seed Oil*, Persea Gratissima Oil, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil, Tocopherol (Vitamin E), Opuntia Ficus Indica Seed Oil*,  Butyrospermum Parkii Butter, Parfum (Natural), Citral, Geraniol, Linalool, Limonene, Citronellol, Eugenol\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e*COSMOS Certified Organic Ingredient\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIngredients of natural origin: 100%\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe list of ingredients may be changed. Please see the packaging for the updated and most accurate list of ingredients.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eparaben-free \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e sulphate-free \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e silicone-free \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e alcohol-free \u003cspan\u003e| EU allergen-free\u003c\/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e| \u003c\/span\u003evegan \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e cruelty-free \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e hand-made \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e with a minimal list of ingredients\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Magrada Organic Cosmetics","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49583851962695,"sku":null,"price":7.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/magrada-lip-balm-melissa-10g-788892.png?v=1739897255","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/magrada-lip-balm-melissa-10g","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}